{
  "texts": [
    "Generative AI models break down prompts into textual representation and logic to parse the tasks required of them.",
    "As users add specificity and context to a prompt, this provides additional logic to guide the model toward desirable outputs (Giray, 2023).",
    "However, our work underscores that outputs from the same prompt are often not deterministic.",
    "In our case, scoring of prompt output revealed high variance in scores within prompt groups (Figure 1).",
    "Simply by chance, some outputs from the same prompt missed over 25% of scoring criteria while others were over 90% complete."
  ]
}